# 👩‍💼 Employee Performance Dashboard

## 📌 Project Overview

This project is an Employee Performance Dashboard created using Microsoft Power BI to analyze employee data and performance metrics.

## 📊 Dataset

* Employee Data
* Performance Data
  (Common column: EmployeeID)

## 🎯 Objectives

* Analyze employee performance
* Track productivity and overtime
* Provide data-driven insights

## 📈 Visualizations Used

* Bar Chart
* Column Chart
* Line Chart
* Pie Chart
* Donut Chart
* Cards
* Slicers

## 🛠 Tools Used

* Microsoft Power BI
* Excel / CSV

## 🔗 Data Model

* One-to-Many relationship using EmployeeID

## 🧠 Insights

* High overtime increases productivity
* Department-wise performance varies
* Top performers identified

